90
00:04:27,950 --> 00:04:28,810
Mengapa kita ada di sini?

91
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:30,390
Orang yang mengirimkan perak ke Xia Jingshi

92
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:32,230
melalui Agen Pendamping Rongtong

93
00:04:32,230 --> 00:04:33,070
