102
00:05:26,750 --> 00:05:28,240
Ruyan sudah punya janji hari ini.

103
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,270
Kenapa tidak biarkan aku?

104
00:05:29,310 --> 00:05:30,490
menemanimu minum-minum?

105
