210
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:27,390
Tuan Muda, tolong jangan menatap tajam ke arahku.

211
00:09:27,420 --> 00:09:28,840
Kamu membuatku takut.

212
00:09:29,190 --> 00:09:32,140
